===Completed Objective Example===
Start with <nowiki><s></nowiki> and close off at <nowiki></s></nowiki> to strike through the objective.

For example:

<pre>
{{ToDo1}}
{{ToDo2
|<s>Complete to-do list guide</s>
|{{complete}}<br>{{complete}}<br>{{complete}}
|[[User:Example1|Example1]]<br>[[User:Example2|Example2]]<br>[[User:Example3|Example3]]
}}
|}
</pre>

The coding above will appear as the template below upon publishing or previewing.


{{ToDo1}}{{ToDo2|<s>Complete to-do list guide</s>|{{complete}}<br>{{complete}}<br>{{complete}}|[[User:Example|Example1]]<br>[[User:Example|Example2]]<br>[[User:Example|Example3]]}}
|}
